     SuperscriptBox["\[PartialD]", "n"], "X"}]}], TraditionalForm]],
  FormatType->TraditionalForm,ExpressionUUID->
  "00028828-6fec-464d-9e60-ff22f48333a1"],
 " one point function on the disk when m,n are positive integer."
}], "Text",
